|archive-date=2021-02-26
|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226181751/https://mollybrown.org/denvers-hop-alley-and-chinatown/
|dead-url=no
}}</ref>。约3000暴民烧毁了唐人街的大部分建筑，也杀死了一位在Sing Lee洗衣店打工的Lu Yang (陆扬)
<ref>{{cite news
